snippet.title: Alice Closet servers are now online! The PV of "Alice Closet" Premiers Now!
snippet.description:
Register now to experience the game before the official release: 
http://www.alice-closet.com/
Alice Closet Closed Beta Registration has begun! All character were designed by Arina Tanemura. A dream of fantasy and love awaits you.
Expected game launch date: mid-June.
